---
const tiers = [
  {
    name: "算力环境部署",
    mode: "一次性实施费",
    desc: "含私有模型部署、微调、内网环境调试及混合云架构设计。"
  },
  {
    name: "软件 CLI 化适配",
    mode: "按软件复杂度",
    desc: "针对专业桌面软件，执行 7 阶段自动化管道、包含完整测试套件。"
  },
  {
    name: "系统接口化适配",
    mode: "按适配器数量",
    desc: "针对 Web 系统（OA/CRM），包含适配器生成、验证及环境安全配置。"
  },
  {
    name: "Agent 平台集成",
    mode: "弹性定制",
    desc: "整合所有工具至 CLI-Hub，并生成 SKILL.md 技能库供 AI 调用。"
  }
];
---

<section class="bg-dark py-24 px-4 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">服务范畴与<span class="text-gold">合作模式</span></h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">所有服务项目均支持分阶段迭代，助力企业以最小试错成本进入 AI 化轨道。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl">
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-white/10 bg-gold/5">
              <th class="p-6 text-gold text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">服务项目</th>
              <th class="p-6 text-gold text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">交付模式</th>
              <th class="p-6 text-gold text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">业务明细说明</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-gray-300">
            {tiers.map(tier => (
              <tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors group">
                <td class="p-6 font-bold text-white group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">{tier.name}</td>
                <td class="p-6 text-sm">{tier.mode}</td>
                <td class="p-6 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">{tier.desc}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-gold/5 text-center text-xs text-gray-400">
        所有商业合作均通过详细业务评估后确定具体落地路径，确保 100% 交付确定性。
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-6 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gold/20 bg-gold/5">
         <span class="text-gold font-bold">💡 核心护城河：</span>
         <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">为您积累的专属企业技能库（SKILL.md）是无法被复制的数字化资产。</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
